org.eclipse.nvplayout.model

Class Calibration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.nvplayout.model.Calibration

  • public class Calibration
extends java.lang.Object
    Calibration is the global model for the calibration view.
    This model contain the global configuration, i-e :
    • Number of block present in calibration.
    • The start address of the calibration memory section.
    • The reference of the different memory block.

    Based on a MVC model

    Version:
    0.0 Alpha EarlyAccess Beta Tester
    Author:
    GLI feat Software Team
    See Also:
    CalibrationBlock
